- Create a tutor/ folder with: engine.ts, logic_graph.ts, retriever.ts, llm.ts, profiling.ts, models.ts, flow.ts, templates/.
- LLM calls must live only in tutor/llm.ts with a provider-agnostic interface.
- chat-kaleb.ts must not import OpenAI/Gemini directly.
- Engine API: tutorOnce(q, attempt, profile) -> structured JSON (no UI text).
- Step templates live in tutor/templates/*.json and responses must be valid per schema.
- No business logic in UI/streaming handlers.
- Add light unit tests where feasible.
